article.description: Maggie Lucas scored 26 points and Alex Bentley had 23 to help Penn State rout Nevada 103-65 on Saturday night in the championship game of the John Ascuaga's Nugget Classic.
article.headline: Maggie Lucas, Alex Bentley key Penn State's rout of Nevada
article.linkText: Lucas, Bentley key Penn State's rout of Nevada
article.story:
RENO, Nev. --  Maggie Lucas scored 26 points and Alex Bentley had 23 to help Penn State (No. 16 ESPN/USA Today, No. 17 AP) rout Nevada 103-65 on Saturday night in the championship game of the John Ascuaga's Nugget Classic.

Zhaque Gray added 21 points for Penn State (5-1).

Kate Kevorken, Danika Sharp and Kayla Williams each had 14 points for Nevada (2-3).

Penn State led 49-34 at the half and had a 62-18 scoring advantage inside the paint.
